Class JSRProvider

java.lang.Object
javax.json.spi.JsonProvider
com.bfo.json.JSRProvider
public class JSRProvider extends JsonProvider

The JsonProvider implementation that provider the JSON-P (JSR374) implementation. See JsonProvider for documentation relating to this class.
